Global Air Skids Market Insights
Air Skids Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Air Skids Market Overview
The air skids market is projected to witness significant growth, with an estimated market value of approximately USD 5 billion by 2030, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% during the forecast period from 2023 to 2030. This growth is attributed to the increasing demand for air skids in various industrial applications, including transportation, military, and energy sectors. Air skids are gaining popularity due to their ability to efficiently transport heavy loads and sensitive equipment across various terrains. The market is driven by technological advancements, rising demand for logistics solutions, and the adoption of air skids in emerging markets.

